Antonio Conte on John Terry:&quot;It was a great privilege for me to be the coach of a Chelsea legend like John Terry.<br />
<br />
&quot;He helped me a lot in my first season in and out of the pitch. He was very important in the training ground .I will never be able to thank him enough.&quot;

Christian Pulisic: &quot;I want to learn to be even more clinical in front of goal continue to boost my numbers, get more goals and assists.<br />
<br />
&quot;I want to be stronger on the ball, being able to hold off players and those are two areas that I'm definitely working on.&quot;

